race.comment: I'M OPINIONATED (10) was simply too good for her rivals last start at Port Macquarie, breaking her maiden by 1.4L in impressive fashion. Suspect they'll adopt similar tactics today from a good draw and  the drop in trip shouldn't be an issue. Can be prominent in the run and build on her last start win. GOLDEN GALAXY (13) wasn't far away last start at Bowraville and that effort stacks up in this event. Drawn nicely over his preferred distance and if he can produce his best, then he'll be in this for a long way. SKATES ON (3) disappointed on a Heavy deck at Kempsey last start but was better prior to that. Back onto a firmer surface today and see him turn in  a much better effort. BRAZEN BRANDO (6) is next best.
